DISCIPLINARY CASES

2005-0398. Disciplinary Counsel v. Watson.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing by relator, Disciplinary Counsel, of a motion for order to appear and show cause.

Upon consideration thereof, it is ordered by this court that relator’s motion is granted. It is further ordered that respondent shall appear in person before this court on September 7, 2011, at 9:00 a.m.

O’Donnell, J., dissents.
